---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - FormatFuse"
  description="Learn how FormatFuse protects your privacy. All file processing happens on your device - we never upload your files."
>
  
  <main class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-transparent to-primary/5"></div>
    
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">Effective Date: June 23, 2025</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-gray dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Welcome to FormatFuse</h2>
            <p>
              FormatFuse is operated by RayLabs Pte. Ltd., a company registered in Singapore. We're committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about our practices. The best part? <strong>Your files never leave your device</strong>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Our Privacy-First Approach</h2>
            <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">üîí Everything Happens on Your Device</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
                <li><strong>No file uploads</strong> - Your files are never sent to our servers</li>
                <li><strong>100% browser-based processing</strong> - All conversions happen locally using WebAssembly</li>
                <li><strong>Zero data retention</strong> - We can't access, store, or see your files</li>
                <li><strong>Complete privacy</strong> - Your sensitive documents stay on your device</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What Information We Collect</h2>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Analytics Data</h3>
            <p>
              To improve FormatFuse and understand how our tools are used, we collect anonymous analytics data using:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong>SimpleAnalytics</strong> - A privacy-first analytics tool that:
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 mt-2">
                  <li>Never collects personal data or uses cookies</li>
                  <li>Doesn't require consent banners or privacy notices</li>
                  <li>Is 100% GDPR compliant by design</li>
                  <li>Only tracks anonymous usage metrics like page views and referrers</li>
                </ul>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong> - Helps us understand user interactions through session recordings and heatmaps
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              <strong>Important:</strong> These analytics tools only track how you interact with our website interface. They cannot and do not access the contents of any files you process.
            </p>

            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
            <p>When you visit FormatFuse, we automatically collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Browser type and version</li>
              <li>Operating system</li>
              <li>General location (country/region level)</li>
              <li>Pages visited and tools used</li>
              <li>Time spent on pages</li>
              <li>Referring website</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the analytics data we collect to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Improve our tools and user experience</li>
              <li>Fix bugs and technical issues</li>
              <li>Understand which tools are most popular</li>
              <li>Optimize website performance</li>
              <li>Develop new features based on usage patterns</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Cookies</h2>
            <p>
              FormatFuse uses minimal cookies:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>SimpleAnalytics</strong> - Does not use any cookies or collect personal data</li>
              <li><strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong> - Uses cookies for session recordings and heatmaps</li>
              <li><strong>Theme preferences</strong> - Stores your light/dark mode preference locally in your browser</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect your experience with some features of the site.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Data Security</h2>
            <p>
              Since all file processing happens in your browser and we never receive your files, your data is inherently secure. For the analytics data we do collect, we use industry-standard security measures to protect it.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>
              We use the following third-party services:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>
                <strong>Umami</strong> - 
                <a href="https://umami.is/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong> - 
                <a href="https://privacy.microsoft.com/privacystatement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>
              FormatFuse is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Your Rights</h2>
            <p>
              Since we don't collect personal information beyond anonymous analytics, there's no personal data for us to share, sell, or retain. You always maintain complete control over your files.
            </p>
            <p>
              If you have any questions about the analytics data we collect, you can contact us at any time.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
              We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Effective Date."
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="space-y-4 mt-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
              If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at:
            </p>
            <p>
              <strong>RayLabs Pte. Ltd.</strong><br />
              Website: <a href="https://raylabs.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">raylabs.io</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-lg p-6 mt-12">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">üìù TL;DR</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 list-disc pl-6">
              <li>‚úÖ Your files never leave your device - everything is processed locally</li>
              <li>‚úÖ We don't upload, store, or access your files</li>
              <li>‚úÖ We use SimpleAnalytics (no cookies, no personal data) and Clarity for analytics</li>
              <li>‚úÖ No personal data collection beyond basic analytics</li>
              <li>‚úÖ FormatFuse is operated by RayLabs Pte. Ltd. (Singapore)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
